A. Project Overview
Problem Statement: E-commerce businesses struggle with inventory accuracy across multiple sales channels and warehouses, leading to overselling and stock discrepancies.

Real-World Use Case: A retailer selling on Amazon, eBay, and their own website needs a centralized inventory system that syncs stock levels in real-time and prevents overselling.

Target Users: E-commerce businesses, inventory managers, warehouse operators, and developers integrating inventory systems.

B. Tech Stack
Language: TypeScript

Framework: NestJS

Database: MongoDB with Mongoose

Cache: Redis

Message Queue: RabbitMQ

API Documentation: Swagger/OpenAPI 3.0

Tools: Docker, Jest, Winston, Prometheus, Grafana
